    "type": "message",
    "text": "So true. A close friend of mine is just getting into software. He’s a former electrical engineer who worked at Bell Labs in the 70's on some really cool stuff - the man’s sharp as they come. But trying to explain how to set up a network so he could control his circuits from his phone… He was just lost, and understandably so. It’s just nuts how complex it all is.",
